  "title": "Landscape Supervisor",
  "description": "<p>· Responsible to deploy manpower for daily landscape maintenance duties and attend to urgent cases when necessary.</p>\n<p>· Responsible to keep track and schedule for daily landscape maintenance accordingly and understand the quality of duties required by the Superior.</p>\n<p>· Able to handle machinery and equipment such as hedge trimmers, chainsaws, long arm pruner, blower, etc.</p>\n<p>· In charge and understand the safety requirements when working outside and inside working areas.</p>\n<p>· Able to demonstrate the basic knowledge in Horticulture Maintenance such as proper pruning methods for shrubs and trees,daily maintenance duties which include watering, fertilizing, weeding, mulching, planting, plant removal etc, protect trees and plants from diseases and insect infestations and planting works.</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work      with Landscape Designer, Supervisor, Salesperson and Customer to review      and install/implement Landscape projects, based on contract.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>· Supervise crew on Landscape projects.</p>\n<p>Requirements</p>\n<p>· Required language(s): English, Chinese (in order to deal with complaints from Chinese speaking client on site)</p>\n<p>· Dynamic and energetic</p>\n<p>· Good team player with ability to lead and multi-task</p>\n<p>· Committed to work</p>\n<p>· Required Skill(s): Microsoft Office</p>\n<p>· Excellent interpersonal and communication skills</p>\n<p>· Prefer candidates with horticulture or arborist knowledge</p>\n<p>· On-the-job training provided</p>\n<p>· Entry level candidates with the relevant Polytechnic / WSQ Diploma / Degree are welcomed</p>\n<p>Working Hours and Office Location:</p>\n<p>· 5.5-day work week</p>\n<p>· Office location: Mandai Estate</p>\n<p>· Work location: Various Sites</p>",
